relation: Darrow1 - #87 With the Foppies now extinct, Paula sets her sights on rescuing the Mr. Saturn. Poor Bob...we hardly knew ye.

Darrow1 - #88 The encounter with Belch draws near and a sinister face pops up to try and scare little children. Unfortunately for Giygas, he's a little too crazy to realize his minions are not as reliable as they seem.
Darrow1 - #89 Belch is a pretty bad guy, not just because he's made of barf, but because he also likes to pick on kids. Also, he is kind of bad at running a factory.

Darrow1 - #90 With Bob gone, Belch's factory is as good as unmanageable. To top it off, downing his favorite snack is even a bigger deal than stopping the destruction of his workplace. This guy just doesn't have his priorities straight.
Darrow1 - #91 This Fly Honey craze borderlines on addiction. Hopefully in between the time he's reborn as Master Barf, Belch will get the proper counseling he needs.
